title: Mens Jeans Skinny Stretch Premium High Rise Colored Jeans Expandable Waist
description: AMAZING STRETCHY: these skinny jeans are extremely elastic and offer relaxed mobility without any restrictions. they have lots of stretchy so your body will not feel any pressure all day long. not too tight, not too loose, with just the right amount of fabric.

BEST-FITTING: you will look more fashion and confident when you snug into these jeans, the elastic waist fits most of the body types. if you are a weight lifter, this is the pair of jeans which will fit your lifestyle.

THEY WERE MADE TO LAST: we use natural and healthy fabrics, high quality smooth zipper, nice cutting and functional pocket design. you can fit your entire hand into these pockets and put your phone inside for better care.

WORK TO WEEKEND WEAR: such a skinny stretch jeans goes well with any shirts, t-shirts, pullovers and jackets, best match to white sneakers. it always catches peoples eyes' and you will get asked where you got them. model is 189cm, 89kg, wearing size 51.
SIZE ATTENTION: model is 6'1"(189cm), 196lb(89kg) wearing size 32 for jeans. This is a skinny jeans, tight fit from ankle to hem. Please go one size up for slim fit.
